        <section id="introduction" class="section">
            <h2>Introduction to Peripheral Devices</h2>
            <p>Peripheral devices are hardware components that connect to a computer to expand its functionality. These devices fall into various categories, such as input devices, output devices, and storage devices. Whether you are typing a document, watching a movie, or saving files, peripheral devices play a crucial role in enhancing your computing experience.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="types" class="section">
            <h2>Types of Peripheral Devices</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Keyboard">
