                        <h3>Input Devices</h3>
                        <p>Devices like keyboards, mice, and graphic tablets that help you input data into your computer.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Monitor">
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Output Devices</h3>
                        <p>Monitors, projectors, and printers that display or output information processed by your computer.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="External Storage">
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Storage Devices</h3>
                        <p>External hard drives, USB drives, and SD cards used to store large amounts of data.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
